    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/2f4f0fae55277318b9e075b93bd9b935.avif?t=1737119825\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras_big/2f4f0fae55277318b9e075b93bd9b935.avif?t=1737119825 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong><br><br>Grimstone Survivors 演示版中等待着您的内容？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grimstone Survivors 是一款提供无限可玩性的 3D Roguelite 游戏！演示版将包含 10-15 个关卡，我们会根据您的反馈继续开发。新更新即将推出！如果您喜欢我们的游戏，欢迎加入我们的 Discord 频道并分享您的想法。同时，不要忘记将其加入您的愿望清单！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D自上而下roguelite体验：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3D自上而下深度射击游戏为roguelite类型注入了新的活力。在这场冒险中，死亡不是终点，每一个新的开始都会让你变得更加强大。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.poster.avif?t=1737119825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.webm?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/6f5f28c92f6ffd637d82eeba44a0cff1.mp4?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略武器组合：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 双手各持不同武器，根据自己的游戏风格塑造战场。使用远程武器从远处追击敌人，而另一只手则使用近战武器为突然袭击做好准备。每种武器组合都具有不同的战略优势，快来发现最致命的武器组合吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.poster.avif?t=1737119825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.webm?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/bace55bc13ddc9547f97c186b50e845c.mp4?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >个性化技能树：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从各种技能中进行选择，形成自己独特的游戏风格。无论你是增加体力的生命消耗专家，还是用快速攻击消灭敌人，你选择的每种技能都会让你独一无二。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.poster.avif?t=1737119825\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.webm?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/5afbc9d66592afba8368923c6d0fabd8.mp4?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满活力和惊喜的战场：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 短期事件可以在眨眼之间扭转战局。通过使用炮塔或生命塔来获得对敌人的战术优势。巧妙利用战场是生存的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.poster.avif?t=1737119825\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.webm?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/423459a5e365531a54458bd74205899b.mp4?t=1737119825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战略资源管理:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 市场为您提供不同的路径。从市场上购买临时能量补充剂可立即获得优势。明智地管理资源将帮助您在充满挑战的关卡中生存下来。<br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入愿望清单:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏开发过程中，将我们的游戏加入您的愿望清单来支持我们。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
